<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Caso Clínico — Reneé | Semiologia Psiquiátrica</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

/* ===========================================
   THEME: ANATÔMICO SOMBRIO
   Dark Botanical · Cormorant + IBM Plex Sans
   =========================================== */
:root {
  --bg: #0f0f0f;
  --bg-2: #141414;
  --text: #e8e4df;
  --text-2: #b0aba4;
  --muted: #6a6560;
  --muted-2: #3a3530;
  --accent-warm: #d4a574;
  --accent-pink: #c4888d;
  --accent-gold: #b09070;
  --accent-pale: #9a9590;
  --red-muted: #8a3030;

  --font-display: 'Cormorant', serif;
  --font-body: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;

  --title-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  --h2-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
  --h3-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
  --body-size: clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
  --small-size: clamp(0.6rem, 1vw, 0.8rem);

  --slide-padding: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  --content-gap: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 2rem);
  --element-gap: clamp(0.25rem, 1vw, 1rem);

  --ease: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}

/* ===========================================
   VIEWPORT BASE (MANDATORY)
   =========================================== */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html, body { height: 100%; overflow-x: hidden; }

html {
  scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  background: var(--bg);
}

body { font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--text); background: var(--bg); }

.slide {
  width: 100vw;
  height: 100vh;
  height: 100dvh;
  overflow: hidden;
  scroll-snap-align: start;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  position: relative;
  background: var(--bg);
}

.slide-content {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  max-height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: var(--slide-padding);
  padding-left: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 9rem);
}

img, .image-container { max-width: 100%; max-height: min(50vh, 400px); object-fit: contain; }

@media (max-height: 700px) {
  :root { --slide-padding: clamp(0.75rem, 3vw, 2rem); --content-gap: clamp(0.4rem, 1.5vw, 1rem); --title-size: clamp(1.25rem, 4.5vw, 2.5rem); --h2-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.75rem); }
}
@media (max-height: 600px) {
  :root { --slide-padding: clamp(0.5rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem); --content-gap: clamp(0.3rem, 1vw, 0.75rem); --title-size: clamp(1.1rem, 4vw, 2rem); --body-size: clamp(0.7rem, 1.2vw, 0.95rem); }
  .nav-dots, .keyboard-hint, .decorative { display: none; }
}
@media (max-height: 500px) {
  :root { --slide-padding: clamp(0.4rem, 2vw, 1rem); --title-size: clamp(1rem, 3.5vw, 1.5rem); --h2-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem); --body-size: clamp(0.65rem, 1vw, 0.85rem); }
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after { animation-duration: 0.01ms !important; transition-duration: 0.2ms !important; }
  html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
}

/* ===========================================
   GLOBAL DECORATIVE ELEMENTS
   =========================================== */

/* Thin vertical accent line on the left */
.accent-line {
  position: absolute;
  left: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 5.5rem);
  top: 8%; bottom: 8%;
  width: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--accent-warm) 20%, var(--accent-warm) 80%, transparent);
  opacity: 0.4;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Abstract blurred orbs for atmosphere */
.orb {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(90px);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.orb-r { background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(100,30,30,0.6) 0%, transparent 70%); }
.orb-p { background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(80,30,60,0.5) 0%, transparent 70%); }
.orb-g { background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(40,50,30,0.4) 0%, transparent 70%); }
.orb-b { background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(30,30,60,0.5) 0%, transparent 70%); }

/* Slide counter in the corner */
.slide-counter {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
  right: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem);
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  line-height: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}

/* Section label top right */
.section-tag {
  position: absolute;
  top: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  right: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--small-size);
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}

/* ===========================================
   ANIMATIONS: REVEAL SYSTEM
   =========================================== */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(22px);
  transition: opacity 0.75s var(--ease), transform 0.75s var(--ease);
}
.reveal-left {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateX(-25px);
  transition: opacity 0.75s var(--ease), transform 0.75s var(--ease);
}
.reveal-blur {
  opacity: 0;
  filter: blur(8px);
  transition: opacity 1s var(--ease), filter 1s var(--ease);
}

.slide.visible .reveal,
.slide.visible .reveal-left,
.slide.visible .reveal-blur {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: none;
  filter: none;
}

.slide.visible .reveal:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.05s; }
.slide.visible .reveal:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.18s; }
.slide.visible .reveal:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
.slide.visible .reveal:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.42s; }
.slide.visible .reveal:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.54s; }
.slide.visible .reveal:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: 0.66s; }
.slide.visible .reveal:nth-child(7) { transition-delay: 0.78s; }

/* Stagger utility — applies delay to children */
.stagger > * { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); transition: opacity 0.65s var(--ease), transform 0.65s var(--ease); }
.slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(1) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay: 0.1s; }
.slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(2) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay: 0.22s; }
.slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(3) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay: 0.34s; }
.slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(4) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay: 0.46s; }
.slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(5) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay: 0.58s; }
.slide.visible .stagger > *:nth-child(6) { opacity:1; transform:none; transition-delay: 0.70s; }

/* ===========================================
   TYPOGRAPHY COMPONENTS
   =========================================== */
.eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--small-size);
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  margin-bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);
}

.display-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 11vw, 9.5rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 0.88;
  color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.display-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent-pink); }

.section-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  margin-bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
}
.section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent-warm); }

.slide-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);
}

.lead {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.6rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--accent-pale);
  line-height: 1.55;
  max-width: 55ch;
}

.body-text {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--body-size);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #c0bbb5;
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 55ch;
}

/* Thin horizontal rule */
.rule {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
  margin: clamp(0.8rem, 2vw, 1.5rem) 0;
}
.rule-line { flex: 1; max-width: clamp(40px, 8vw, 100px); height: 1px; background: var(--muted-2); }
.rule-dot { width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent-warm); flex-shrink: 0; }

/* Pull quote style */
.pull-quote {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-warm);
  padding-left: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
  margin: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem) 0;
}
.pull-quote p {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.pull-quote cite {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--small-size);
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

/* Symptom / finding tag */
.tag {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.25em 0.7em;
  border: 1px solid var(--muted-2);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: clamp(0.55rem, 0.8vw, 0.7rem);
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.tag.accent { border-color: var(--accent-warm); color: var(--accent-warm); }
.tag.pink { border-color: var(--accent-pink); color: var(--accent-pink); }

/* Two-column layout */
.two-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem);
  align-items: start;
}
@media (max-width: 700px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* Finding item (symptom lists) */
.finding-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  gap: clamp(0.4rem, 1vw, 0.8rem);
}
.finding-list li {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--body-size);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #b0aba4;
  padding-left: 1.2em;
  position: relative;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.finding-list li::before {
  content: '—';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  font-size: 0.85em;
}
.finding-list li strong {
  color: var(--text);
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* Diagnosis block */
.diag-block {
  background: rgba(212,165,116,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(212,165,116,0.2);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: clamp(0.8rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem) clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.6rem);
}
.diag-block .label {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--small-size);
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.diag-block .value {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.3;
}

/* Meta grid (identificação, etc.) */
.meta-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: clamp(0.5rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem) clamp(1rem, 2vw, 2rem);
}
@media (max-width: 600px) { .meta-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
.meta-item .meta-label {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: clamp(0.55rem, 0.8vw, 0.65rem);
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
}
.meta-item .meta-val {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--body-size);
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text);
}

/* EEM section card */
.eem-card {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--muted-2);
  padding-top: clamp(0.6rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);
  margin-top: clamp(0.6rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);
}
.eem-card:first-child { border-top: none; margin-top: 0; padding-top: 0; }
.eem-card .eem-heading {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--small-size);
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent-warm);
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
}
.eem-card p {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--body-size);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #b0aba4;
  line-height: 1.55;
}

/* Syndrome pill */
.syndrome-pill {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.4em 1em;
  background: rgba(196,136,141,0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(196,136,141,0.3);
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--body-size);
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--accent-pink);
}
.syndrome-pill.warm {
  background: rgba(212,165,116,0.1);
  border-color: rgba(212,165,116,0.3);
  color: var(--accent-warm);
}
.syndrome-pill.muted {
  background: rgba(154,149,144,0.08);
  border-color: rgba(154,149,144,0.2);
  color: var(--accent-pale);
}

/* ===========================================
   PROGRESS BAR
   =========================================== */
.progress-bar {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent-warm), var(--accent-pink));
  width: 0%;
  transition: width 0.3s ease;
  z-index: 100;
}

/* ===========================================
   NAV DOTS
   =========================================== */
.nav-dots {
  position: fixed;
  right: clamp(0.8rem, 1.5vw, 1.5rem);
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
  z-index: 100;
}
.nav-dot {
  width: 5px; height: 5px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--muted-2);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}
.nav-dot.active {
  background: var(--accent-warm);
  transform: scale(1.4);
}

/* ===========================================
   ===  SLIDE 01 — CAPA  ===
   =========================================== */
#s01 .orb-1 {
  width: clamp(250px, 45vw, 600px); height: clamp(250px, 45vw, 600px);
  top: -15%; right: -10%;
}
#s01 .orb-2 {
  width: clamp(180px, 30vw, 380px); height: clamp(180px, 30vw, 380px);
  bottom: -5%; left: -8%;
}
#s01 .slide-content {
  padding-bottom: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  justify-content: flex-end;
}
#s01 .top-header {
  position: absolute;
  top: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  left: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 9rem);
  right: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem);
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
}
#s01 .top-header .course {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--small-size);
  letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}
#s01 .top-header .fonte {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--small-size);
  color: var(--muted);
  text-align: right;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ===========================================
   ===  SECTION DIVIDER SLIDE  ===
   =========================================== */
.section-divider .slide-content {
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: center;
}
.section-num {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 16rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 0.8;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  position: absolute;
  right: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 3rem);
  bottom: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 2rem);
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>
<nav class="nav-dots" id="navDots" aria-label="Navegação de slides"></nav>

<!-- ============================================================
     SLIDE 01 — CAPA
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="slide" id="s01" aria-label="Capa">
  <div class="orb orb-r orb-1"></div>
  <div class="orb orb-p orb-2"></div>
  <div class="accent-line"></div>

  <div class="top-header">
    <span class="course reveal-blur">Semiologia Psiquiátrica · Curso de Medicina</span>
    <span class="fonte reveal-blur">Sechehaye, M. — Grune &amp; Stratton, 1951</span>
  </div>

  <div class="slide-content">
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) minmax(260px,32%); gap:clamp(1.5rem,4vw,4rem); align-items:start;">

      <!-- BLOCO PRINCIPAL -->
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Caso Clínico Psiquiátrico</p>

        <h1 class="display-title reveal">Re<em>née</em></h1>

        <div class="rule reveal">
          <div class="rule-dot"></div>
          <div class="rule-line"></div>
        </div>

        <p class="lead reveal">
          Análise semiológica de síndrome esquizofrênica paranoide<br>
          com elementos de desorganização e catatonia.
        </p>

        <div style="display:flex; gap:0.6rem; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:clamp(1.2rem,2.5vw,2rem);" class="reveal">
          <span class="tag accent">Síndrome Esquizofrênica</span>
          <span class="tag">Paranoide · Desorganizada · Catatônica</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- BLOCO ALUNOS -->
      <div class="reveal" style="
        border-left:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
        padding-left:clamp(1rem,2vw,1.5rem);
        align-self:center;
      ">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:0.8rem;">Alunos</p>

        <div style="
          display:flex;
          flex-direction:column;
          gap:0.45rem;
          font-size:clamp(.88rem,1vw,1rem);
          line-height:1.45;
          color:var(--muted);
          letter-spacing:.02em;
        ">
          <span>Ana Ruth</span>
          <span>Arielly Morais</span>
          <span>Beatriz Senna</span>
          <span>Crisanny Duarte</span>
          <span>Igor Silvério</span>
          <span>Ingrid Sarmento</span>
          <span>Rodrigo Carneiro</span>
          <span>Tayssa Façanha</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="slide-counter">01</div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     SLIDE 02 — IDENTIFICAÇÃO
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="slide" id="s02" aria-label="Identificação">
  <div class="orb orb-p" style="width:clamp(200px,35vw,420px);height:clamp(200px,35vw,420px);top:-10%;right:-5%;"></div>
  <div class="orb orb-g" style="width:clamp(150px,20vw,280px);height:clamp(150px,20vw,280px);bottom:0;left:20%;"></div>
  <div class="accent-line"></div>
  <span class="section-tag">1 — Identificação</span>

  <div class="slide-content">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">1. Identificação</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Quem é <em>Reneé?</em></h2>
    <div class="rule reveal"><div class="rule-dot"></div><div class="rule-line"></div></div>

    <div class="meta-grid reveal stagger">
      <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-label">Nome</div><div class="meta-val">Reneé</div></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-label">Idade</div><div class="meta-val">20 anos</div></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-label">Sexo</div><div class="meta-val">Feminino</div></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-label">Estado Civil</div><div class="meta-val">Solteira</div></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-label">Escolaridade</div><div class="meta-val">Fundamental completo</div></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><div class="meta-label">Procedência</div><div class="meta-val">Genebra, Suíça</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="pull-quote reveal" style="margin-top:clamp(1.2rem,2.5vw,2rem);">
      <p>"Eu me sentia separada de tudo. As coisas deixavam de existir de verdade. As pessoas se tornavam bonecos, autômatos — eu as conhecia, mas não as reconhecia como vivas."</p>
      <cite>Queixa principal</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="slide-counter">02</div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     SLIDE 03 — HDA PARTE 1 (infância e adolescência)
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="slide" id="s03" aria-label="História da Doença Atual — início">
  <div class="orb orb-r" style="width:clamp(180px,30vw,380px);height:clamp(180px,30vw,380px);top:5%;right:5%;"></div>
  <div class="accent-line"></div>
  <span class="section-tag">2 — HDA</span>

